ent payment security for credit card transactions. With online payments, you must route your customers  credit card data through many layers of security. Shopify handles that aspect as well, processing credit card transactions securely and guaranteeing payment.","<strong>All-in-one Platform</strong><br/>Another reason Shopify is so popular with  Shark Tank  contestants, is that it is simple to use. Building a user-friendly eCommerce website and making sure all of the pieces are in place can be challenging. You most likely want certain key features such as integrated payments, a user-friendly way to add and delete products, a tool to track payments and inventory, and the ability to personalize the website to your liking.","<strong>Design</strong><br/>Designing your website is a breeze. Shopify has three levels of customization. It provides free themes that are easy for you to use. The benefit is that you don t need professional web designer to customize your online store. Not only does Shopify provide free themes you can choose from, but also it has custom themes that you can purchase. Shopify allows you to build a personalized eCommerce platform at the click of a button.","<strong>Marketing</strong><br/>Marketing is a huge issue when you start up an online business, and new entrepreneurs may feel at sea. Shopify provides tools that help you create landing pages a home page for your website. Also for search engine optimization (SEO), Shopify provides webmaster tools and sitemaps. It creates clean code and allows title tags and meta descriptions to help search engines find your site for potential customers.","<strong>Customer Service</strong><br/>Shopify has a big database that provides FAQs, phone support, and email and live chat support. You never have to feel that you are in a situation without answers. Shopify customer support representatives are incredibly knowledgeable and helpful. Regardless of the problem or question you have, with Shopify; you can get credibl